column5: Hey all, it's been a long time since I've had a fishing report...I may just get one out next week.  My vacation begins as soon as I finish my shift tomorrow after noon at 1:30pm  I am hoping to get out for a bit on Pigeon Lake, Georgian Bay, Nippising and Sturgeon Bay..  With any luck I'll get a chance to catch up with a few people  Maureen
Sounds familiar Mo. Good luck and enjoy your holidays.
YER GETTING HOLIDAYS? LOL  Have a great time MO.
Get out and hammer them Maureen!! Looking forward to a report!
